# Chat screenshots

When the user mentions a screenshot, screen capture, or "look at this image":

1. Check `.cursor/chat-screenshots/latest.png` first (updated by `npm run screenshot`).
2. Read that file with the Read tool — it supports PNG/JPG/WebP.
3. If missing, tell them: Win+Shift+S → `npm run screenshot` → in chat type `@` → select `latest.png`.

Do not ask them to paste into chat if `@` attach fails — the file path workflow is the supported fallback on Windows.
